  <h2>Installing Steam</h2>
  
    <ol type="1">
      <li>Turn on the computer and monitor</li>
      <li>Open the internet browser</li>
      <li>Search for steam on Internet Explorer</li>
      <li>Go to the steam website</li>
      <li>Click on download on the website and follow the steps provided</li>
    </ol>  
    
  <h2>Installing Avast Antivirus</h2>
  
    <ol type="1">
      <li>Turn on the computer and monitor</li>
      <li>Open the internet browser</li>
      <li>Search for Avast on Internet Explorer</li>
      <li>Go to the Avast website</li>
      <li>Click Download Free Antivirus</li>
      <li>Follow the Three steps to download Avast</li>
    </ol>

